******* Terms and Conditions *********

I (emavisuals) built the ImmaginAI app (the app) as a free app. This app is provided by me at no cost and is intended for use as is.

ImmaginAI is an that can be used to generate digital images from a given text input (prompt).

You will need to type and share a text input in order to use the app and generate the image. You are not allowed to use or generate any post banned, illegal, racist, violent or offensive content. 
The app and its creator are not responsible for any content that you generate, nor how you will use said content. The model usual delivers content corresponding
to the descriptions given as a prompt, but this is not guaranteed. 

I, the creator of this app, reserve the right, in my sole discretion, to modify, limit or discontinue any aspect and functionality of Subscribers Explorer at any time.
You cannot sell, modify, copy or alter in any way the app and its functionalities, nor delegate someone else to do it for you.
The app is not affiliated with any other product or service.


